<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٨٠ الحروف المستهجنة<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٨٢ صفات الحروف ومخارجها<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
